Collection: The Arab Institute - Abu Dis Collection

Title: مقال منشور عن مدرسة المعهد العربي
AltTitle.other: A Published Article Regarding the Arab Insitute
Description.note: A one-page document which includes a published article in al-Quds Newspaper written about the "Arab Institue" in Abu Dis, this institute contains a department for orphans, this department can accommodate ninety students.  This institute receives three annual scholarships from the state of Kuwait, and receives three scholarships from the faculty of Science and Technology.|~|وثيقة مكونة من صفحة واحدة تتضمن مقال منشور في جريدة القدس عن مدرسة المعهد العربي حملت عنوان "مدرسة المعهد العربي في "أبوديس" تضم قشماً لرعاية الايتام يستوعب تسعين طالبا تحصل سنويا على ست ممنح من الكويت ومن كلية العلوم.
References: Ozrail, Samar, "The Arab Institute – Abu Dis Collection," archival inventory, October 2018, the Palestinian Museum Digital Archive.
Series & Collection: The Arab Institute - Abu Dis Collection | Arab Institute - Abu Dis Sub-collection 2: Documents and Papers

AltTitle.other: A Notebook Used to Register the Proceedings of the Private Schools Committee's Session in al- Quds "Jerusalem"
Description.note: A document consists of several pages, where the proceedings of the Private Schools Committee's Session are registered, this committee was found in 1985 in the city of al-Quds "Jerusalem", it was established to tackle and encounter the oppressive practices and policies of the Israeli Occupation against the educational system in the 1967 Occupied Palestinian Territory.|~|وثيقة مكونة من عدة صفحات تتضمن وقائع جلسات لجنة المدارس الخاصة التي تشكلت في عام 1985 في مدينة القدس وهدفت إلى مواجهة سياسيات القمع الصهوينية لنظام التعليم في الأراضي الفلسطينية المحتلة عام 1967.
References: Ozrail, Samar, "The Arab Institute – Abu Dis Collection," archival inventory, October 2018, the Palestinian Museum Digital Archive.
